article:
__NOTOC__ Year '1973' ('[[Roman numerals|MCMLXXIII]]') was a common year
starting on Monday (link will display the full calendar) of the Gregorian
calendar. It was also the 1973rd year of the Common Era, the 973rd year of
the 2nd millennium, the 73rd year of the 20th century, and the 4th year of
the 1970s.
